      <title>美国提名Leo Brent Bozell III为南非大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-nominates-leo-brent-bozell-iii-as-ambassador-to-south-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政府已提名保守派活动家和作家利奥·布伦特·博泽尔三世（Leo Brent Bozell III），成为该国驻南非大使。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-nominates-leo-brent-bozell-iii-as-ambassador-to-south-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的司法敌人是卡瓦诺（Kavanaugh）的室友，得到了共和党的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-judicial-foe-was-kavanaugh-s-roommate-had-gop-s-backing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，法官是“激进的左疯子”，应该受到弹each。总检察长说他正在保护恐怖分子。司法部律师说，法官对政府的裁决正在破坏委内瑞拉帮派成员的重要努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-judicial-foe-was-kavanaugh-s-roommate-had-gop-s-backing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>州州告诉法官，特朗普仍然没有解开所有联邦资金。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-still-not-unfreezing-all-federal-funds-states-tell-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群由民主党领导的州再次指责唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府违反了法院命令，未能释放数百万美元的联邦灾难资金，这是白宫混乱的一月支出冻结的最新诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-still-not-unfreezing-all-federal-funds-states-tell-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼说，加拿大希望与特朗普在贸易谈判中“认真”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/carney-says-canada-wants-to-get-serious-with-trump-on-trade-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）说，他的顶级内阁部长正在与白宫官员接触，并希望就贸易进行“认真的”谈判，因为美国贸易伙伴为唐纳德·特朗普总统的下一份关税打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/carney-says-canada-wants-to-get-serious-with-trump-on-trade-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC主席提名保罗·阿特金斯（Paul Atkins），配偶至少价值3.27亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/sec-chair-nominee-paul-atkins-spouse-worth-at-least-327-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的披露，唐纳德·特朗普总统的提名人保罗·阿特金斯（Paul Atkins），唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领导证券交易委员会（Securities and Commission），其配偶的总净资产至少为3.27亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/sec-chair-nominee-paul-atkins-spouse-worth-at-least-327-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:30:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国看到俄罗斯，乌克兰选择更长的战争而不是一笔不良交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/russia-ukraine-see-unsatisfactory-ceasefire-worse-than-continued-war-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国情报界的一项评估，俄罗斯和乌克兰可能会看到更大的动力延长三年冲突，而不是急于达成完整的解决方案，该评估与唐纳德·特朗普总统的承诺迅速结束了为期三年的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/russia-ukraine-see-unsatisfactory-ceasefire-worse-than-continued-war-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在记者透露也门罢工聊天后支持华尔兹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对白宫国家安全顾问迈克尔·沃尔兹（Michael Waltz）表示信心，因为助手无意中将总编辑纳入了大西洋的主编，该助理是在一个短信小组中，内容涉及对也门的军事罢工计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 13:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫拒绝在利雅得披露俄罗斯 - 美国谈话的细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/kremlin-refuses-to-disclose-details-of-russia-us-talks-in-riyadh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，俄罗斯和乌克兰已同意在黑海进行休战，并制定了实施禁止对能源基础设施的罢工的机制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/kremlin-refuses-to-disclose-details-of-russia-us-talks-in-riyadh</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列批准预算，给内塔尼亚胡政治喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/israel-set-to-pass-budget-in-political-respite-for-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会批准了今年的国家预算，在与加沙冲突和试图解雇高级官员的政府有关的市场动荡之后，促进了总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/israel-set-to-pass-budget-in-political-respite-for-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 10:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其资产反弹，因为Simsek发誓要恢复稳定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/turkey-finance-czar-will-meet-investors-to-ease-pressure-on-lira</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当高级经济官员试图向外国投资者保证上周拘留伊斯坦布尔市长Ekrem Imamoglu时，土耳其的债券和股票反弹，这一举动触发了数十亿美元的外流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/turkey-finance-czar-will-meet-investors-to-ease-pressure-on-lira</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 04:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
